The OPTIMADE API has been developed with contributions by the participants of the workshops "Open Database Integration for Materials Design", held at:
- the Lorentz Center in Leiden, Netherlands from 2016-10-24 to 2016-10-28
- the CECAM in Lausanne, Switzerland from 2018-06-11 to 2018-06-15
- the CECAM in Lausanne, Switzerland from 2019-06-11 to 2019-06-14
- the CECAM in Lausanne, Switzerland (virtually) 2020-06-08 to 2020-06-12

